Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.83,0:28:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,downloading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.22,0:28:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And with all this information,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.89,0:28:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we are looking forward to seeing
