Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.36,0:28:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.57,0:28:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to join the Apple MFi
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.72,0:28:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Program.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.53,0:28:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to join the Apple MFi
